{"tid":28633,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"星座撚入嚟估我星座","createTime":"2016-12-08T05:25:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-24T03:45:54.000Z","uid":29601,"like":16,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ae5f81d5d941acb4f150c75c94b5b98cc0200437","tid":28633,"uid":29601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:25:23.000Z","msg":"既然你哋講到每個星座都有特定性格 咁你哋試下由我性格推斷出我星座<br />\n每人可以問我最多三條問題 太私隱嘅嘢就唔好問啦<br />\n然後你哋可以估我星座<br />\n不過估中我唔會講 由你哋繼續估 到無人覆我就會統計下究竟有幾多人係真係估得中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c491fd945bbc4d7e8039c32c7ccf77d6f002b9f","tid":28633,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:26:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ee788a9102c17e4b3159b5fb3b9a91c32e5e8a34","tid":28633,"uid":29601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:28:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>估中都唔會講，大家咪撚覆。</blockquote><br />\n去到無人覆我會開個新post講呀 我想睇下你哋有幾多人真係估得中"},{"pid":"d1800b8d0ff6d575a8d5cc16d9a7bc3b4abb8c2e","tid":28633,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:35:03.000Z","msg":"唔洗問都知你係處"},{"pid":"2cbd962370a227f923ad8c00ea094e82fa3492a0","tid":28633,"uid":29676,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:35:45.000Z","msg":"星座撚真係好無聊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔通同一星座嘅人會有同一性格？<br />\n成日都話好準啊呢個超準啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n準你條命<br />\n最戇鳩就係話自己唔會同xx座嘅人拍拖<br />\n你老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 根本性格同星座冇關係<br />\n係你睇太多星座嘢洗哂腦<br />\n覺得自己個星座應該要點點點<br />\n自己圍住佢轉 變埋嗰種性格咋"},{"pid":"5dca9fce6aaf1c760675fec6b635ac15bf1baff3","tid":28633,"uid":4725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:36:27.000Z","msg":"有冇潔辟/強迫症？"},{"pid":"f6a913eb2ee50751a8b5c58db3c5b49847998411","tid":28633,"uid":29601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:40:41.